needs.name: feel inspired to create and explore new sounds.
causes: to engage with other artists and producers online
to receive feedback on experimental tracks shared on platforms like SoundCloud or Bandcamp
to follow and interact with innovative music trends on social media
to participate in online forums and discussions about music production techniques
to explore music streaming services for new and diverse genres
to watch tutorials and creative process videos on YouTube
to use virtual reality or AI-based tools to experiment with soundscapes and environments
to attend live-streamed concerts and DJ sets for fresh inspiration

needs.name: experience validation and recognition for their work.
maintain creativity despite challenges or setbacks.
develop resilience to handle criticism and rejection.
feel connected to a community of like-minded individuals.
achieve a sense of accomplishment in project completion.
cultivate patience for long hours and detailed work.
nurture passion for music to keep motivation high.
sustain focus during repetitive and technical tasks.
express emotions and personal experiences through music.
experience growth through continuous learning and adaptation.
